snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Chaos Gate - Daemonhunters Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Warhammer 40,000: Chaos Gate - Daemonhunters, a turn-based tactics game and long awaited sequel to 1998's Chaos Gate -  puts players in command of a squad of elite Grey Knights on a quest to rid the galaxy of Chaos.
